  "detailed_description": "LillyMonster is a horror survival game where you must survive and bring Lilly outside.<br>You play as the \"guardian\", and you lead Lilly along.<br><br>LillyMonster is a mix of genres. It blends the basic concept of escaping a horror maze, with strategic planning and resource management. This is achieved through \"Lilly\".<br><br>Lilly is a cute, yet \"troubled\" girl.<br>As you progress through the level, she has certain demands.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sometimes, she is hungry.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926790/extras/1fbee04cb98282536c2e5ff5f4134efc.poster.avif?t=1670990038\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926790/extras/1fbee04cb98282536c2e5ff5f4134efc.webm?t=1670990038\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926790/extras/1fbee04cb98282536c2e5ff5f4134efc.mp4?t=1670990038\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sometimes, she wants to take a nap.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926790/extras/da05a68fcc4b16dcd6ee88753d63865c.poster.avif?t=1670990038\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926790/extras/da05a68fcc4b16dcd6ee88753d63865c.webm?t=1670990038\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926790/extras/da05a68fcc4b16dcd6ee88753d63865c.mp4?t=1670990038\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sometimes, she wants to sing.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926790/extras/d0c6887f9b234cbfeb2075d2bfc7c36b.poster.avif?t=1670990038\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926790/extras/d0c6887f9b234cbfeb2075d2bfc7c36b.webm?t=1670990038\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926790/extras/d0c6887f9b234cbfeb2075d2bfc7c36b.mp4?t=1670990038\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>If you fail to plan ahead, pay attention to her cues, or simply lack the resources, she will cause chaos that attracts the rival towards you.<br>If you are a good \"guardian\", everything will be fine.<br><br>Your job as a player, is to unlock the final door, while deciding how to manage Lilly.<br><br>She’s a very unique character with many annoyances, making her come to life in a cute and playful fashion.<br><br>So what are you waiting for? Lilly wants to play...<br><br>Features:<br>1 gamemode whereby you manage Lilly and attempt to deliver all 7 eggs while avoiding the rival",
  "about_the_game": "LillyMonster is a horror survival game where you must survive and bring Lilly outside.<br>You play as the \"guardian\", and you lead Lilly along.<br><br>LillyMonster is a mix of genres. It blends the basic concept of escaping a horror maze, with strategic planning and resource management. This is achieved through \"Lilly\".<br><br>Lilly is a cute, yet \"troubled\" girl.<br>As you progress through the level, she has certain demands.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sometimes, she is hungry.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926790/extras/1fbee04cb98282536c2e5ff5f4134efc.poster.avif?t=1670990038\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926790/extras/1fbee04cb98282536c2e5ff5f4134efc.webm?t=1670990038\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926790/extras/1fbee04cb98282536c2e5ff5f4134efc.mp4?t=1670990038\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sometimes, she wants to take a nap.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926790/extras/da05a68fcc4b16dcd6ee88753d63865c.poster.avif?t=1670990038\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926790/extras/da05a68fcc4b16dcd6ee88753d63865c.webm?t=1670990038\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1926790/extras/da05a68fcc4b16dcd6ee88753d63865c.mp4?t=1670990038\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sometimes, she wants to sing.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_